### Employee API — Requisições HTTP
### Porta: 8087

### ============================================================
### Listar todos os funcionários
### ============================================================
GET http://localhost:8087/api/employees
Accept: application/json

### ============================================================
### Buscar funcionário por ID
### ============================================================
GET http://localhost:8087/api/employees/1
Accept: application/json

### ============================================================
### Criar funcionário — Sucesso
### ============================================================
POST http://localhost:8087/api/employees
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Pedro Souza",
  "email": "pedro.souza@email.com",
  "cpf": "222.333.444-55",
  "salary": 6500.00,
  "departmentId": 1
}

### ============================================================
### Criar funcionário — Salário abaixo do mínimo (422)
### ============================================================
POST http://localhost:8087/api/employees
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Teste Salário",
  "email": "teste.salario@email.com",
  "cpf": "333.444.555-66",
  "salary": 1000.00,
  "departmentId": 1
}

### ============================================================
### Criar funcionário — Email duplicado (409)
### ============================================================
POST http://localhost:8087/api/employees
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Ana Duplicada",
  "email": "ana.silva@email.com",
  "cpf": "444.555.666-77",
  "salary": 5000.00,
  "departmentId": 1
}

### ============================================================
### Criar funcionário — Validação (nome curto, email inválido) (400)
### ============================================================
POST http://localhost:8087/api/employees
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "AB",
  "email": "email-invalido",
  "cpf": "12345678900",
  "salary": -100,
  "departmentId": 1
}

### ============================================================
### Criar funcionário — Departamento inexistente (404)
### ============================================================
POST http://localhost:8087/api/employees
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Teste Departamento",
  "email": "teste.dept@email.com",
  "cpf": "555.666.777-88",
  "salary": 5000.00,
  "departmentId": 999
}

### ============================================================
### Atualizar funcionário
### ============================================================
PUT http://localhost:8087/api/employees/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Ana Silva Atualizada",
  "email": "ana.silva@email.com",
  "cpf": "123.456.789-09",
  "salary": 9500.00,
  "departmentId": 1
}

